title: NFL ATL: Schedule Release Extravaganza!
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Schedule Release Extravaganza!
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- reveals the 2014 NFL schedule!  Don’t miss out as the gang breaks down all of the biggest matchups and storylines in the season ahead.
